---
title: Cheesy Mexican-Spiced Beef & Radish Salsa with Rice & Aioli
description: Red is the colour of passion and we sure are passionate about what’s going into this bowl. Fall head over heels for the beef strips
and feel those heart palpitations for the garlic aioli. Take a deep breath and relax your tastebuds with a fluffy rice to cool off.
